    <para id="import-auto-id1169033119310">Your eighty-three-year-old grandmother has been using a computer for some time now. As a way to keep in touch, you frequently send emails of a few lines to let her know about your day. She calls after every email to respond point by point, but she has never emailed a response back. This can be viewed as an example of:</para><list id="fs-id1452250" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
